Private Sub AbaAlmHistorico_Click()
On Error GoTo ErrHandler
Dim INSTRUMENTO_1 As String Dim INSTRUMENTO_2 As String Dim INSTRUMENTO_3 As String Dim INSTRUMENTO_4 As String
